# Trominal Testing

Full skill: [testing.md](mdc:.ai/skills/testing.md)

## Coverage thresholds (CI enforced)

- Backend (Pest): **≥80%**
- Client TS (Vitest): **≥70%**
- Rust (tarpaulin): **≥60%**
- Cross-platform crypto fixtures: **100%** (golden file parity)

## What to test

- **Every endpoint:** happy path + auth required + validation errors + ownership enforcement
- **Every service method:** all branches
- **Every policy:** allow + deny
- **Single-user mode race condition:** parallel registration
- **Audit log writes** for sensitive actions
- **Encrypted casts** round-trip correctly

## What NOT to test

- ❌ Framework code (TanStack Query internals)
- ❌ Types (TS does that)
- ❌ Trivial getters/setters
- ❌ Tests that mirror implementation rather than verify behavior

## Flaky test policy

- Flaky test → quarantine within 24h with TODO + issue link
- Fix or delete within 1 sprint
- No `--retry` to mask flakes
